text_en:
I am almost certain.
Time flows differently here
than in the outside world…{END}

This space is something like
a cocoon for them
to store up power…{END}

The space is complete…
My servants will build
perfect darkness.{END}

Yes. He is probably the mastermind
who created this mutation space
and revived the kaijin…{END}

Right… But they can cross time,
while we are scattered
through different eras…{END}

Anything done in this space
must immediately affect
this timeline.{END}

A revived army of kaijin,
and a mighty enemy
stirring behind them.{END}

They scheme across every era,
trying to rewrite
the history of humanity.{END}

Standing against them are
Kamen Rider 1, V3, BLACK,
and Agito.{END}
